OL,6,FMore than 100 schools in England with
OL,7,Fwill have blocks rebuilt or
OL,8,Frefurbished under the government's
OL,9,Frebuilding programme, the Department
OL,10,Ffor Education (DfE) has said.
OL,12,FThe Department has published details
OL,13,Fon how it will permanently remove
OL,14,Freinforced autoclaved aerated concrete
OL,15,F(Raac) from all across the country.
OL,17,FIt comes after a school leaders' union
OL,18,Fcalled on the government to provide
OL,19,Fmore financial support to schools
OL,20,Ffacing ongoing issues as a result of
OL,21,FRaac.
