OL,6,FA total of 234 education settings in
OL,7,FEngland have been identified as having
OL,8,FRaac in some areas of their buildings,
OL,9,Fwhich is a slight rise on the 231
OL,10,Freported in November.
OL,12,FThe DfE has said that 119 of these
OL,13,Fschools will have one or more
OL,14,Fbuildings rebuilt or refurbished
OL,15,Fthrough the government's School
OL,16,FRebuilding Programme as works to
OL,17,Fremove Raac are more extensive or
OL,18,Fcomplex.
