OL,6,FA further 110 schools and colleges `
OL,7,Fwhere works will typically be smaller
OL,8,Fin scale ` will receive a grant to
OL,9,Fhelp them remove Raac from their
OL,10,Fbuildings.
OL,12,FFive schools and colleges have
OL,13,Falternative arrangements in place to
OL,14,Faddress the removal of Raac, the DfE
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan
OL,18,Fsaid: "Nothing is more important to me
OL,19,Fthan the safety of every child and
OL,20,Fmember of staff in school.
