OL,6,FLast month Geoff Barton, general
OL,7,Fsecretary of the Association of School
OL,8,Fand College Leaders (ASCL), sent an
OL,9,Fopen letter to the education secretary
OL,10,Fcalling for schools with Raac to be
OL,11,Fexempt from Ofsted inspections until
OL,12,Fthey were "fully operational".
OL,14,FA school or college that has confirmed
OL,15,FRaac on site will be eligible for an
OL,16,Finspection this term, but they can ask
OL,17,Ffor an inspection to be deferred.
