OL,6,FIn a letter to Ms Keegan, Mr Barton
OL,7,Fsaid managing Raac was still creating
OL,8,F"major issues" for schools ` including
OL,9,Flack of access to specialist equipment
OL,10,Fand limited or no catering facilities.
OL,12,FLast month, the ASCL called on
OL,13,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt to introduce in
OL,14,Fhis Spring Budget a new recovery
OL,15,Ffunding stream ` which could be used
OL,16,Ffor catch-up provision ` for all the
OL,17,Fschools affected by Raac.
