OL,6,FThe union warned in its submission to
OL,7,Fthe Treasury that an "unacceptable"
OL,8,Fwait for mitigation works at Raac-
OL,9,Faffected schools meant parents were
OL,10,Fwithdrawing their children and moving
OL,11,Fthem to different schools, and
OL,12,Fapplications for September 2024 for
OL,13,Fthese affected schools were down.
OL,15,FFollowing the DfE's announcement on
OL,16,FThursday, Mr Barton said: "We welcome
OL,17,Fthis much-needed clarity on the nature
OL,18,Fof the work to remove Raac from the
OL,19,Fschools and colleges affected.
