OL,6,F"This is an important step, but it is
OL,7,Fonly one step towards solving this
OL,8,Fcrisis and a number of unanswered
OL,9,Fquestions remain.
OL,11,F"Given the severe pressures on the
OL,12,Fschool estate as a whole, we need
OL,13,Fassurances that this work will be
OL,14,Ffunded wholly through additional
OL,15,Fcapital expenditure and money will not
OL,16,Fbe diverted from other sources.
OL,18,F"There must also be clear timelines
OL,19,Fset out for when this work is going to
OL,20,Fbe completed.
